data.description: New paint and flooring inside.  Updated kitchen.  Totally new updated bathroom.  Newer vinyl windows on the main level.  The Main level other room (9 X 6) is laundry space and storage on the main level.  The other room (13 X 14) in the basement has a walkout and could be almost anything.  There is a 24 X 12 Conex Box in the backyard that the seller has used as a garage and storage building.  It WILL BE INCLUDED in the sale.  PPRBD website shows: New electric service upgrade 2023, roof in 2017, furnace in 2006, water heater 2023 (no permit).
